<body lang=ZH-CN style='text-justify-trim:punctuation' scroll="yes">
<div class=Section1>

<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
        <td height="60" align="center"><b>Form of Advance Bond of Overseas Project Contracting</b></td>
    </tr>
</table>
<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-autospace:none'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US>To:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;color:red'><%if(map.get("BFNM") != null){out.print((String)map.get("BFNM"));}%></span></b><span
lang=EN-US>Date:</span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;color:red'><%if(map.get("ISDT") != null){out.print((String)map.get("ISDT"));}%></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:楷体_GB2312'>No:</span><b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;color:red'><%if(map.get("LCNO") != null){out.print((String)map.get("LCNO"));}%></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US>Dear Sirs,</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US>Whereas the </span><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;color:red'><%if(map.get("APNM") != null){out.print((String)map.get("APNM"));}%></span></b><span lang=EN-US>(hereinafter
called the contractor) has entered into a contract for -------(name of the
project) (hereinafter called the project)at ----with ------- (name of the
beneficiary) (hereinafter called the employer).Whereas the employer has agreed
to advance to the contractor at his request an amount of</span><b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;color:red'><%if(map.get("LCCY") != null){out.print((String)map.get("LCCY"));}%> <%if(map.get("LCAM") != null){out.print((String)map.get("LCAM"));}%></span></b><span
lang=EN-US> (Say------only), whereas the employer has required the contractor
to furnish a guarantee with an amount equal to the above said advance payment
and for performance of his obligation concerned with the advance payment under
the contract, and whereas the</span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;
color:red'><%if(map.get("ADBKNM") != null){out.print((String)map.get("ADBKNM"));}%></span></b><span lang=EN-US>(name of the
bank)(hereinafter called the surety) at the request of the contractor and in
consideration of the employer agreeing to make the above mentioned advance to
the contractor, has agreed to furnish the above required guarantee.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US>Now herefore, the surety do hereby
guarantee that the contractor shall utilize the above said </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US>advance for the purpose of the project
and if he fails and commits default in fulfillment of any of his obligation for
which the advance payment is made, it shall entitle the employer to be paid not
exceeding the above mentioned amount. Against notice in writing of any default,
which the surety shall be given by the employer stating that the contractor has
failed to fulfil</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US>its obligation to the
employer and upon such first demand, payment shall be made by the surety of the
sum then due under this guarantee without any objection.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US>The guaranteed sum shall be automatically
and proportionally reduced in the step of the progress of the project. The
surety's liability under this guarantee shall not in any case exceeding the sum
of</span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;color:red'><%if(map.get("LCCY") != null){out.print((String)map.get("LCCY"));}%> <%if(map.get("LCAM") != null){out.print((String)map.get("LCAM"));}%></span></b><span
lang=EN-US>only.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US>This guarantee shall become effective
from the date of receipt of the advance by the contractor and valid until </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;color:red'><%if(map.get("EPDT") != null){out.print((String)map.get("EPDT"));}%></span></b><span
lang=EN-US> upon expiry, please return this guarantee to us for cancellation.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-right:3.6pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:楷体_GB2312'>For </span><span
lang=EN-US>China Construction Bank</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:left;
text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:楷体_GB2312'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-autospace:none'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-autospace:none'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体'>&nbsp;</span></p>

